g.text: Do not remove any tiles from play
You may not reveal more than 4 tiles
North to South on a row.
- All players on the starting tile
* Pay 1 gold, ride the train up to 3 tiles.
* When you reveal a tile, if you are doing this
the furthest West yet, gain 3 VP.
* When you clear a tile of bandits, gain 3 dice's
